Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:06.80,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}君と一緒なら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.91,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}未来之事
